messages.message:
@Abhishek Adupa I’m happy to handle this in a fork and then submit to you for review and merging. I’ll do 2 tasks:
• Change names of Postman calls so they’re the same as the names we use in `openapi.yaml` and the docs
• Change the order of the Postman calls so they mirror the order used in the docs (the consistency will make things easier for users to find, even though I can understand why Postman currently does things like carving off some of the operations into an “Advanced” section that the docs don’t have.
